yrus">麦莉·赛勒斯</a>（ <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/miley-cyrus-says-house-burnt-down-filming-black-mirror-episode-3494054">她的房子显然在拍摄剧集时被烧毁</a>）、萨尔玛·海耶克（她<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/salma-hayek-was-worried-black-mirror-role-would-get-her-in-trouble-3457095">担心她的剧集会给她带来“麻烦”</a> ）和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/aaron-paul">亚伦·保尔</a>， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/black-mirror-reveals-season-six-casts-aaron-paul-josh-hartnett-and-kate-mara-all-feature-3268592">在其他人中</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/black-mirror-fans-spot-hidden-message-in-season-seven-teaser-trailer-3601999">《黑镜》粉丝发现第七季预告片中隐藏的信息</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
