</script></p><p> “免费户外表演和我迄今为止最重要的公告，”帖子中写道。 “3 月 18 日星期一。北伦敦。周一上午 10 点发布我的故事的确切地点。演出时间为下午 5 点。来伦敦吧。到时候那里见。快要变得精神错乱了。”</p><p>如前所述，演出地点要到演出当天早上才能确定，而腕带将从下午 3 点开始在相关地点提供。</p><p>在一周前发布的原始预告视频中，Yungblud 表示：“10 天后，我们将发布迄今为止最重大的公告，但在此之前，在那天之前，每天下午 5 点，我们将发布我认为有助于塑造和定义这个社区的记忆。”</p><p>随后，他分享了第一次这样的记忆，那是在 2019 年 7 月的一次约会中<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-yungblud-cause-mayhem-river-thames-explosive-show-2533171">，当时他和 150 名粉丝在泰晤士河上的一艘船上举行了即兴演出。</a>一场喧闹的表演结束后，他将一句“被低估的年轻人有希望”（There’s Hope For The Undergraduate Youth）投影到议会大厦的一侧，这是对他当时的单曲的引用。</p><p> 1 月，Yungblud 发行了他的最新单曲《When We Die (Can We Still Get High?)》，这是继 2023 年发行的一系列三首单曲之后推出的：六月的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/yungblud-returns-to-his-roots-and-launches-new-era-with-lowlife-3452594">《Lowlife》</a> 、八月的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/yungblud-opens-up-about-being-molested-as-a-child-ahead-of-new-single-hated-3487618">《Hated》</a> ——Yungblud 将其描述为“他发行过的最个人化的歌曲”，以及他十月份发行的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/yungblud-teams-up-with-bring-me-the-horizons-oli-sykes-on-new-single-happier-3517063">“Happier”</a> 。后一首歌曲由<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bring-me-the-horizon">Bring Me The Horizo​​n</a>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/oli-sykes">Oli Sykes</a>演唱，这是两人继<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/bring-me-the-horizon-and-yungblud-obey-review-2743512">Yungblud 2020 年单曲《Obey》</a>之后的第二次合作。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/yungblud-teases-free-outdoor-show-in-london-next-week-ahead-of-biggest-announcement-yet-its-about-to-get-fookin-mental-3601981">在“迄今为止最重大的公告”之前，Yungblud 的帖子预告了下周在伦敦举行的免费户外表演：“It&#39;s about to get fookin mental”</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
 Guns N' Roses：“Iggy Pop 让我度过了一次糟糕的蘑菇之旅” https://www.nme.com/news/music/guns-n-roses-iggy-pop-got-me-through-a-bad-mushroom-trip-3601948?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=guns-n-玫瑰伊吉流行音乐让我经历了一次糟糕的蘑菇之旅Anagricel DuranFri, 15 Mar 2024 18:07:14 +0000 Music NewsNewsRockhttps://www.nme.com/?p=3601948 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Guns-N-Roses-Duff-McKagan-and-Iggy-Pop.-Credit-Tim-Mosenfelder-and-FABRICE-COFFRINI-via-Getty.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="枪花乐队的达夫·麦卡根和伊基·波普。图片来源：Tim Mosenfelder 和 FABRICE COFFRINI，来自 Getty" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Guns-N-Roses-Duff-McKagan-and-Iggy-Pop.-Credit-Tim-Mosenfelder-and-FABRICE-COFFRINI-via-Getty.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Guns-N-Roses-Duff-McKagan-and-Iggy-Pop.-Credit-Tim-Mosenfelder-and-FABRICE-COFFRINI-via-Getty-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Guns-N-Roses-Duff-McKagan-and-Iggy-Pop.-Credit-Tim-Mosenfelder-and-FABRICE-COFFRINI-via-Getty-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Guns-N-Roses-Duff-McKagan-and-Iggy-Pop.-Credit-Tim-Mosenfelder-and-FABRICE-COFFRINI-via-Getty-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Guns-N-Roses-Duff-McKagan-and-Iggy-Pop.-Credit-Tim-Mosenfelder-and-FABRICE-COFFRINI-via-Getty-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Guns-N-Roses-Duff-McKagan-and-Iggy-Pop.-Credit-Tim-Mosenfelder-and-FABRICE-COFFRINI-via-Getty-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “我全程看了伊基，只是迷幻药太多了。但他让我失望了”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/guns-n-roses-iggy-pop-got-me-through-a-bad-mushroom-trip-3601948">枪与玫瑰乐队的帖子：“Iggy Pop 让我经历了一次糟糕的蘑菇之旅”</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Guns-N-Roses-Duff-McKagan-and-Iggy-Pop.-Credit-Tim-Mosenfelder-and-FABRICE-COFFRINI-via-Getty.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="枪花乐队的达夫·麦卡根和伊基·波普。图片来源：Tim Mosenfelder 和 FABRICE COFFRINI，来自 Getty" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Guns-N-Roses-Duff-McKagan-and-Iggy-Pop.-Credit-Tim-Mosenfelder-and-FABRICE-COFFRINI-via-Getty.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Guns-N-Roses-Duff-McKagan-and-Iggy-Pop.-Credit-Tim-Mosenfelder-and-FABRICE-COFFRINI-via-Getty-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Guns-N-Roses-Duff-McKagan-and-Iggy-Pop.-Credit-Tim-Mosenfelder-and-FABRICE-COFFRINI-via-Getty-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Guns-N-Roses-Duff-McKagan-and-Iggy-Pop.-Credit-Tim-Mosenfelder-and-FABRICE-COFFRINI-via-Getty-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Guns-N-Roses-Duff-McKagan-and-Iggy-Pop.-Credit-Tim-Mosenfelder-and-FABRICE-COFFRINI-via-Getty-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Guns-N-Roses-Duff-McKagan-and-Iggy-Pop.-Credit-Tim-Mosenfelder-and-FABRICE-COFFRINI-via-Getty-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="/artists/guns-n-roses">Guns N&#39; Roses</a>贝斯手<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/duff-mckagan">Duff McKagan</a>透露了<a href="/artists/iggy-pop">Iggy Pop</a>在他青少年时期如何帮助他度过了一次“糟糕的蘑菇之旅”。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/big-reads/iggy-pop-cover-interview-2022-every-loser-3358737">伊基·波普（Iggy Pop）：“我以为一旦我年满 65 岁，事情就会平静下来。但事实并非如此”</a></strong></li></ul><p>在出现在由<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/spandau-ballet" target="_blank" rel="noopener">斯潘道芭蕾舞团 (Spandau Ballet</a> ) 的加里·坎普 (Gary Kemp) 和受人尊敬的音乐家盖伊·普拉特 (Guy Pratt) 主持的<em>Rockonteurs 播客</em>中时，麦卡根讲述了他 14 岁时发生的事件以及这位前<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-stooges">傀儡乐队</a>主唱如何帮助他摆脱困境。</p><p> “伊基波普让我度过了一次糟糕的蘑菇之旅。我去观看伊吉秀时蘑菇摄入过多，我以为我必须去医院，吓坏了，”马卡根告诉坎普和普拉特。</p><p>他继续说道：“我刚刚看完了《伊基》，只是迷幻剂太多了。但他让我失望了。我已经是伊基的忠实粉丝了，但后来我想，他对我来说意义更大。他是我人生的一个转折点。” </p><p><iframe title="Spotify 嵌入：S6E4：Duff McKagan" style="border-radius: 12px" width="100%" height="152" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen allow="autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; fullscreen; picture-in-picture" loading="lazy" src="https://open.spotify.com/embed/episode/4mlto1YLLZBuvcIlO7JwRe?go=1&#038;sp_cid=72d8e289f4f4e5aaf9d8468db9286e1a&#038;utm_source=oembed&#038;utm_medium=desktop&#038;nd=1&#038;dlsi=c9161fb82e5d4375"></iframe></p><p>这位贝斯手对自己过去的药物滥用问题一直持开放态度，自 1994 年因急性酒精诱发的胰腺炎住院以来，已经清醒了 30 年。</p><p>他此前声称“我没有喝任何水。我刚刚喝了酒。我实际上已经 12 年没有喝过一杯水了。”<a href="/artists/van-halen">范海伦</a>前歌手萨米·哈加尔 (Sammy Hagar) 于 2023 年在后者的<em>摇滚公路旅行</em>电视节目中接受采访时说道。</p><p>去年在接受<a href="https://people.com/guns-n-roses-duff-mckagan-says-prior-to-getting-sober-wasnt-planning-on-living-past-30-exclusive-8399627#:~:text=A%20major%20shift%20in%20McKagan's,but%20that's%20just%20the%20truth." target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《人物》</em></a>采访时，这位贝斯手表示，他的物质问题一开始是恐慌发作的拐杖，而他的健康问题迫使他面对自己的问题。</p><p> “我发现半瓶伏特加可以缓解惊恐发作。问题是，当你开始喝酒然后吸毒时，体内有太多的糖和酒精，而且没有睡眠，所以你会出现更多的惊恐发作。那么你猜怎么着？我越来越多地自行用药，”他说。</p><p>其他新闻方面，麦卡根最近发行了他的第三张录音室专辑“Lighthouse”，其中包括 Pop、他的枪与玫瑰乐队成员<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/slash">Slash</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/alice-in-chains">Alice in Chains 的</a>Jerry Cantrell 等人。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/guns-n-roses-iggy-pop-got-me-through-a-bad-mushroom-trip-3601948">枪与玫瑰乐队的帖子：“Iggy Pop 让我经历了一次糟糕的蘑菇之旅”</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
